                            <comment id="14152474" author="lhofhansl" created="Mon, 29 Sep 2014 23:03:17 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Looking at the patch now... It does not make much sense anyway:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
+&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; [ -z &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;${HBASE_ROOT_LOGGER}&quot;&lt;/span&gt; ]; then
 export HBASE_ROOT_LOGGER=${HBASE_ROOT_LOGGER:-&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;INFO,RFA&quot;&lt;/span&gt;}
+fi
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The existing code (at least in 0.98+) &lt;tt&gt;export HBASE_ROOT_LOGGER=${HBASE_ROOT_LOGGER:&amp;#45;&quot;INFO,RFA&quot;&lt;/tt&gt;} seems to do the right thing already anyway - notice the &lt;tt&gt;${HBASE_ROOT_LOGGER:-&lt;/tt&gt; part, which evaluates to 2nd part only if the variable is null.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;In any case, going to commit the addendum to 0.94 now. &lt;/p&gt;</comment>
